{"tid":339166,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【北京終年毒霧彌漫　肺癌頓成「頭號殺手」】","createTime":"2017-07-28T20:42:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T21:46:36.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a71b3dd5b23a9758e465d947c545b489ce57a71","tid":339166,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T20:42:49.000Z","msg":"中國空氣污染極其嚴重，其中的重災區北京更是終年毒霧彌漫，在這環境下，肺癌成為當地居民因病死亡的「頭號殺手」。<br />\n<br />\n北京市腫瘤防治研究辦公室前日（7月26日）發表《2016年度北京市衛生與人群健康狀況報告》，指2015年北京市戶籍居民確診有惡性腫瘤，發病率較前年增長0.59%。常見癌症當中，肺癌高踞首位，發病率更持續上升。男性當中，肺癌發病率居首位；女性當中，肺癌發病率為第二位。<br />\n<br />\n報告又提到，北京市居民的主要健康指標持續向好，得到顯著提升，與發達國家水平接近。<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-28-2017/40688\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F07-28-2017%2F40688&d=O8Th30%2F6NwmgSi%2BxoenX2oM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=c351108c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-28-2017/40688</a><br />\n<br />\n#毒霧 #霧霾 #北京 #肺癌<br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血文青課金計劃：<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F%3Fview%3Draise2&d=O8Th30%2F6NwmgSi%2BxoenX2oM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=72136876\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise2</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血主持育成計劃：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F%3Fview%3Draise&d=O8Th30%2F6NwmgSi%2BxoenX2oM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=0e2bfb8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise</a><br />\n《熱血時報》 iOS，Android 同步抗共，歡迎下載：<br />\niPhone<br />\n<a href=\"http://goo.gl/bpNcBn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FbpNcBn&d=O8Th30%2F6NwmgSi%2BxoenX2oM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=7516a91e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://goo.gl/bpNcBn</a><br />\nAndroid<br />\n<a href=\"http://goo.gl/IY4fHi\" data-sr-url=\"https://